thread.title: Dean
thread.title_full: Transport Luxury Auto reviewed by Dean

author: Dean
title: Dean
text:
This is the worst transport service I've experienced...ever! My car arrived damaged, the inside was filthy from a greasy driver. Complaint fell on deaf ears. My advice...find someone else to transport your car.
Update...they pulled my bad review claiming I'm a competitor. So that's how they keep their high ratings...blame it on someone else! WOW
